descriptionHTML:
!! Get a Free Manage your Android Wear !!!

You can manage the list of apps installed on your Android Wear.
Wear the app installed on your phone by showing only help so you can easily Launch, Setting Info or delete.
And Running applicaion List on the Android Wear.
You can check Android Wear memory and Kill the application Process.


**** Features ****

* Installed application list that support the Android Wear
- Launch on Wear
- Launch on Phone/Tablet
- Delete
- Go to Application Setting

* Running Applicaion On the Android Wear
- Kill Process
- Check Use/Total Memory



*** Features will be added

Battery Manage !!



So thank you for the feedback about the current beta version features and opinions.
We do not collect any personal information this app
